word_mean_info__list.difference: 一般用词，指服从或接受某种权威，或遵循某种原则而行事。
指顺从或屈服于自己不能进一步抵制或抵抗的人或事物。
指同意依从他人的愿望或请求，或遵守某种规则或顺应某种环境条件。
表示“甘心忍受”，作及物动词时，宾语为反身代词，但一般为不及物动词，后接介词to 。
“投降”，与surrender 大致同义，但是指“温和的让步”。
“投降”，强调“被迫投降，压力很大”，是不及物动词，后接介词to；用作及物动词时，表因战败或被迫“交出”，“放弃”某些事物。

list.abstract: Submit 对象代表 HTML 表单中的一个提交按钮 (submit button)。
submit，英语单词，动词，意为“使服从；主张；呈递；提交；服从，顺从”。

yingyinNormal.en: The university is only allowed to submit one proposal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而我们大学只允许提交一份申请书。

yingyinNormal.en: If you stand by it and submit before it everything is fine, if you are late you lose a percentage grade per day.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你按时提交了论文，那么一切没问题，但如果迟交了，你每天将失去一定的分数。

yingyinNormal.en: Excuse me. I submit the admission is moot.
yingyinNormal.zh: 打断一下，我申请承认无效。

yingyinNormal.en: I would say look this semester you have to submit three papers, you can submit them anytime you want.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我告诉他们，这个学期你们要交三篇论文，你们可以在任意时候交。

yingyinNormal.en: I submit to the court, 10:00. The court laughs in your face.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我提请法院批准，改为晚上十点。法院当着你的面哈哈大笑。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm not going to read them before the end of this semester, but you can submit them anytime you want.
yingyinNormal.zh: 期末之前我都不会批改这些论文，你们想什么时候交都可以。

yingyinNormal.en: We're done here. Call this number and we'll fax you a copy of the report, so you can submit it to your insurance company.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我都问完了，打这个电话，我们会把调查报告传真给你们的，这样你们就能向保险公司索赔了。

yingyinNormal.en: I submit to you, the flier, which never made it onto the refrigerator, where you are supposed to put things, because it was... Yes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我来向你呈上，那张传单，根本没被贴到冰箱上，你本该把重要文件都贴在那里的，因为它... 它...在...找到。

yingyinNormal.en: But here's a trick. You have to commit today to when you are going to submit each of the papers. And these deadlines that you commit to is binding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但有一点要注意今天你们就要决定好每篇论文你计划什么时候交。这些你选择的期限一经确定就不能更改。

yingyinNormal.en: If you have a legitimate request, you can submit it to me in writing, and I'll evaluate it based on its merits. Sure, sure. Is "jet ski" one word or two?
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你们有合理正当的需求，你们可以写一份报告给我，我会根据利弊来评估。行行行，请问水上摩托的"摩"字怎么写？

yingyinNormal.en: What? I'm sorry it didn't go well today. And there's like four things in my inbox that you're perfect for and I will submit you. But right now, you're coming. It will be fun.
yingyinNormal.zh: 干嘛？很遗憾你今天的试镜不是很顺利。我收件箱里有差不多四部戏都非常适合你，我会帮你申请。但是现在，你要和我们一起去。会很有意思的。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, right, sure. So, after I decide, do I then submit it to you for approval, or...? No. You decide, you approve, and then you pride yourself on a job well done. That's a lot of responsibility.
yingyinNormal.zh: 懂了，没问题。在我做了决定之后，我是把决定送交您审核通过，还是...？不用。你决定，你通过，然后你嘉勉自己做得棒棒哒。这责任十分重大啊。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
